name: Bitcoin Uptober
description:
Celebrate Bitcoin's Uptober Mega Bull Run to 100K with a short animated NFT loop. 

This MPG is an animated Bitcoin shaped word cloud, populated using words from Satoshi Nakamoto's original whitepaper  "Bitcoin: A Peer-to-Peer Electronic Cash System"

There's only one thing left to say.... To the Mooooooonnnnnnnn!!!!
